Egg group - MONSTER / MINERAL

The fossilized remains of a snake. The venom has survived thousands of years which has made it even more toxic.
A fossilized basilisk. It can move at a surprising speed given its age. One drop of its venom can kill an elephant. Its frills are made of diamond and taper to a razor-thin edge.
